### 4. FloatingWindowManager - View Binding空指针风险
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/ui/floating/FloatingWindowManager.java`
**行号**: 51-65, 757-775

```java
// forceBlinkRelayoutRunnable
private final Runnable forceBlinkRelayoutRunnable = new Runnable() {
    @Override
    public void run() {
        if (binding == null) {  // ← 检查在handler.post()之后执行
            return;
        }
        // binding在检查和使用之间可能变为null
        View root = binding.getRoot();
        root.setVisibility(View.VISIBLE);  // ← 可能NPE
    }
};

// miniBlinkRunnable同样的问题
```

**问题描述**:
- 在handler.post()调用和run()执行之间，`binding`可能已经被设置为null（通过destroy()）
- 虽然有null检查，但在多线程环境下仍存在竞态条件

**修复建议**:
```java
public void destroy() {
    if (Looper.myLooper() != Looper.getMainLooper()) {
        handler.post(this::destroy);
        return;
    }
    destroyed = true;
    handler.removeCallbacksAndMessages(null);
    // 先hide再清理binding
    hideWindowInternal();
    LayoutFloatingWindowBinding bindingRef = binding;
    binding = null;
    layoutParams = null;
    dragAndClickListener = null;
}
```

