### 5. LogManager/AbnormalRecordManager - 持久化失败无感知
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/data/local/LogManager.java`
**行号**: 130-143

```java
private void persistLocked() {
    try (OutputStreamWriter writer = new OutputStreamWriter(
            new java.io.FileOutputStream(storeFile, false), StandardCharsets.UTF_8)) {
        writer.write(array.toString());
    } catch (Exception ignored) {  // ← 持久化失败被静默忽略
    }
}
```

**问题描述**:
- 磁盘满、文件权限问题等导致持久化失败时用户完全不知情
- 可能导致日志和异常记录在应用重启后丢失

**修复建议**:
```java
private void persistLocked() {
    try (OutputStreamWriter writer = new OutputStreamWriter(...)) {
        writer.write(array.toString());
    } catch (Exception e) {
        android.util.Log.e(TAG, "持久化失败: " + e.getMessage());
        // 可选：尝试写入备用位置
    }
}
```

---

## 🟡 Medium（中优先级，建议关注）

### 6. AbnormalRecordManager.replaceAll() - 重复记录检查效率低
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/data/local/AbnormalRecordManager.java`
**行号**: 79-92

```java
public synchronized void replaceAll(List<AbnormalRecord> records) {
    cache.clear();
    for (AbnormalRecord item : records) {
        if (item == null || containsRecordIdLocked(item.getId())) {  // ← O(n²)复杂度
            continue;
        }
        cache.add(item);
    }
}

private boolean containsRecordIdLocked(String recordId) {
    for (AbnormalRecord item : cache) {  // ← 每次都遍历整个列表
        if (item != null && recordId.equals(item.getId())) {
            return true;
        }
    }
    return false;
}
```

**问题描述**:
- 当records列表很大时，containsRecordIdLocked的O(n)复杂度导致整体O(n²)
- 5000条记录时可能需要2500万次比较

**修复建议**:
```java
private final Set<String> recordIdSet = new HashSet<>();  // O(1)查找

private boolean containsRecordIdLocked(String recordId) {
    return recordIdSet.contains(recordId);
}
```

