### 8. GatewayV2StreamClient - 缺少连接超时配置
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/data/remote/v2/GatewayV2StreamClient.java`
**行号**: 49-57

```java
public GatewayV2StreamClient(@Nullable Context context) {
    client = new OkHttpClient.Builder()
            .pingInterval(20, TimeUnit.SECONDS)
            .retryOnConnectionFailure(true)
            .build();  // ← 缺少connectTimeout
}
```

**问题描述**:
- 没有设置连接超时，可能导致在网络不佳时应用长时间无响应
- Android最佳实践建议设置合理的超时时间

**修复建议**:
```java
client = new OkHttpClient.Builder()
        .connectTimeout(10, TimeUnit.SECONDS)
        .pingInterval(20, TimeUnit.SECONDS)
        .retryOnConnectionFailure(true)
        .build();
```

