## 一、Critical级别问题 (可能导致崩溃/严重功能异常)

### BUG-1: FloatingWindowManager 潜在的WindowManager泄漏风险
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/ui/floating/FloatingWindowManager.java`
**行号**: 202-206
```java
private void hideWindowInternal() {
    // ...
    try {
        windowManager.removeViewImmediate(binding.getRoot());
    } catch (Exception ignored) {
    } finally {
        windowAdded = false;
    }
}
```
**问题描述**: 
- 使用`removeViewImmediate`在finally块中设置`windowAdded = false`，但如果`removeViewImmediate`抛出异常，binding引用可能未被清理
- 在`destroy()`方法(176-187行)中虽然设置了`binding = null`，但如果`hideWindowInternal()`中的异常导致状态不一致，可能导致内存泄漏

**修复建议**:
```java
private void hideWindowInternal() {
    handler.removeCallbacks(forceBlinkRelayoutRunnable);
    handler.removeCallbacks(miniBlinkRunnable);
    miniBlinkActive = false;
    miniBlinkDimmed = false;
    if (!windowAdded || binding == null) {
        minimized = false;
        draggingWindow = false;
        pendingRender = false;
        return;
    }
    View rootView = binding.getRoot();
    try {
        if (rootView != null && rootView.getParent() != null) {
            windowManager.removeViewImmediate(rootView);
        }
    } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {
        // View not attached, ignore
    } catch (Exception ignored) {
    } finally {
        windowAdded = false;
    }
    minimized = false;
    draggingWindow = false;
    pendingRender = false;
}
```

---

### BUG-2: MonitorService 中 ExecutorService 关闭后未置null前被访问的风险
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/service/MonitorService.java`
**行号**: 551-568
```java
private boolean executeOnExecutor(@Nullable ExecutorService executor, Runnable task) {
    if (task == null) {
        return false;
    }
    ExecutorService currentExecutor = executor;
    if (currentExecutor == null || currentExecutor.isShutdown() || currentExecutor.isTerminated()) {
        return false;
    }
    try {
        currentExecutor.execute(task);
        return true;
    } catch (RejectedExecutionException exception) {
        if (logManager != null) {
            logManager.warn("后台任务已跳过，服务正在关闭");
        }
        return false;
    }
}
```
**问题描述**: 
- `isShutdown()`和`isTerminated()`检查与`execute()`调用之间存在竞态条件
- 如果服务在检查和执行之间被销毁，仍可能抛出异常

**修复建议**:
```java
private boolean executeOnExecutor(@Nullable ExecutorService executor, Runnable task) {
    if (task == null) {
        return false;
    }
    ExecutorService currentExecutor = executor;
    if (currentExecutor == null || currentExecutor.isShutdown()) {
        return false;
    }
    try {
        currentExecutor.execute(task);
        return true;
    } catch (RejectedExecutionException exception) {
        if (logManager != null) {
            logManager.warn("后台任务已跳过，服务正在关闭");
        }
        return false;
    } catch (Exception e) {
        // 捕获其他可能的异常
        return false;
    }
}
```

