### BUG-3: AccountStatsPreloadManager 中潜在的NullPointerException
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/runtime/account/AccountStatsPreloadManager.java`
**行号**: 602-603
```java
private boolean matchesSnapshotIdentity(AccountStorageRepository.StoredSnapshot left,
                                        AccountStorageRepository.StoredSnapshot right) {
    if (left == null || right == null) {
        return false;
    }
    return left.getAccount().trim().equalsIgnoreCase(right.getAccount().trim())
            && left.getServer().trim().equalsIgnoreCase(right.getServer().trim());
}
```
**问题描述**: 
- `left.getAccount()`或`right.getAccount()`可能返回null，调用`trim()`会导致NPE

**修复建议**:
```java
private boolean matchesSnapshotIdentity(AccountStorageRepository.StoredSnapshot left,
                                        AccountStorageRepository.StoredSnapshot right) {
    if (left == null || right == null) {
        return false;
    }
    String leftAccount = left.getAccount();
    String rightAccount = right.getAccount();
    String leftServer = left.getServer();
    String rightServer = right.getServer();
    if (leftAccount == null || rightAccount == null || leftServer == null || rightServer == null) {
        return false;
    }
    return leftAccount.trim().equalsIgnoreCase(rightAccount.trim())
            && leftServer.trim().equalsIgnoreCase(rightServer.trim());
}
```

