## 二、High级别问题 (可能导致功能异常/性能问题)

### BUG-4: LogManager 文件操作异常静默处理
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/data/local/LogManager.java`
**行号**: 104-128, 130-143
```java
private void loadFromDisk() {
    synchronized (this) {
        cache.clear();
        if (storeFile.exists()) {
            try (BufferedReader reader = new BufferedReader(...)) {
                // ...
            } catch (Exception ignored) {
                cache.clear();
            }
        }
        // ...
    }
}

private void persistLocked() {
    JSONArray array = new JSONArray();
    // ...
    try (OutputStreamWriter writer = ...) {
        writer.write(array.toString());
    } catch (Exception ignored) {
    }
}
```
**问题描述**: 
- 文件读写异常被静默忽略，可能导致日志丢失或数据损坏时无感知
- `loadFromDisk()`中使用了双重同步（synchronized方法+synchronized块）

**修复建议**:
```java
private void loadFromDisk() {
    cache.clear();
    if (!storeFile.exists()) {
        trimLocked();
        publishLocked();
        return;
    }
    try (BufferedReader reader = new BufferedReader(...)) {
        // ...
    } catch (Exception e) {
        cache.clear();
        // 记录错误日志
        android.util.Log.e("LogManager", "Failed to load logs from disk", e);
    }
    trimLocked();
    publishLocked();
}

private void persistLocked() {
    JSONArray array = new JSONArray();
    // ...
    try (OutputStreamWriter writer = ...) {
        writer.write(array.toString());
    } catch (Exception e) {
        android.util.Log.e("LogManager", "Failed to persist logs", e);
    }
}
```

