### BUG-5: GatewayV2StreamClient WebSocket连接状态竞态条件
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/data/remote/v2/GatewayV2StreamClient.java`
**行号**: 99-151
**问题描述**: 
- `connectInternal()`方法中`socket`字段的读写存在多线程竞态
- `onOpen`回调中设置`socket = webSocket`与外部`disconnect()`可能并发执行

**修复建议**: 已在代码中使用`synchronized`块保护，但建议在`onOpen`中也使用同步块：
```java
@Override
public void onOpen(WebSocket webSocket, Response response) {
    synchronized (GatewayV2StreamClient.this) {
        if (activeConnectionId != connectionId) {
            webSocket.cancel();
            return;
        }
        socket = webSocket;
        reconnectAttempt = 0;
        reconnectScheduled = false;
    }
    notifyState(ConnectionStage.CONNECTED, "已连接");
}
```

