### BUG-6: MonitorService 中lastNotifyAt Map的并发访问问题
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/service/MonitorService.java`
**行号**: 69, 791-794
```java
private final Map<String, Long> lastNotifyAt = new HashMap<>();
// ...
for (String symbol : alert.getSymbols()) {
    if (symbol != null && !symbol.trim().isEmpty()) {
        lastNotifyAt.put(symbol.trim(), now);
    }
}
```
**问题描述**: 
- `lastNotifyAt`是普通的HashMap，在多线程环境下（主线程+后台线程）可能被并发访问
- 可能导致ConcurrentModificationException或数据不一致

**修复建议**:
```java
private final Map<String, Long> lastNotifyAt = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();
```

