## 三、Medium级别问题 (代码质量问题/潜在风险)

### BUG-7: FloatingWindowManager 中dragSlopPx计算可能为0
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/ui/floating/FloatingWindowManager.java`
**行号**: 97
```java
this.dragSlopPx = Math.max(6, ViewConfiguration.get(this.context).getScaledTouchSlop());
```
**问题描述**: 
- 虽然使用了`Math.max(6, ...)`，但如果`ViewConfiguration.get()`返回null（极端情况），会抛出NPE

**修复建议**:
```java
int scaledTouchSlop = 6;
try {
    scaledTouchSlop = ViewConfiguration.get(this.context).getScaledTouchSlop();
} catch (Exception e) {
    // use default
}
this.dragSlopPx = Math.max(6, scaledTouchSlop);
```

