### BUG-8: AbnormalRecordManager JSON解析异常静默处理
**文件**: `app/src/main/java/com/binance/monitor/data/local/AbnormalRecordManager.java`
**行号**: 176-178, 191-195
```java
for (int i = 0; i < array.length(); i++) {
    cache.add(AbnormalRecord.fromJson(array.getJSONObject(i)));
}
```
**问题描述**: 
- `fromJson`可能抛出异常，导致整个加载失败
- 单条记录解析失败不应影响其他记录

**修复建议**:
```java
for (int i = 0; i < array.length(); i++) {
    try {
        JSONObject obj = array.getJSONObject(i);
        if (obj != null) {
            cache.add(AbnormalRecord.fromJson(obj));
        }
    } catch (Exception e) {
        // 记录日志，继续处理下一条
        android.util.Log.w("AbnormalRecordManager", "Failed to parse record at index " + i, e);
    }
}
```

